LAZV-chain/
│
├─ core/                     # Pure blockchain logic (sovereign)
│   ├─ block.py              # Block structure
│   ├─ blockchain.py         # Chain rules, validation, height
│   └─ token.py              # Native LAZV coin logic
│
├─ node/                     # Network layer
│   ├─ seed_node.py          # Full node / producer
│   ├─ light_node.py         # HP / low resource node
│   └─ p2p.py                # Peer discovery & sync
│
├─ polygon/                  # Anchor layer (NOT dependency)
│   ├─ config.py             # Polygon RPC, chainId
│   ├─ polygon_rpc.py        # Low-level RPC sender
│   └─ checkpoint.py         # Send LAZV block hash to Polygon
│
├─ explorer/                 # Read-only tools
│   └─ explorer.html
│
├─ docs/
│   ├─ RUN_NODE.md           # How to run seed/light node
│   ├─ GOVERNANCE.md         # Community rules
│   └─ RECOVERY.md           # If all nodes die
│
├─ README.md                 # Global intro
├─ MANIFESTO.md              # Philosophy (important)
└─ LICENSE                   # MIT
